trans-unit.source: Represents a security token that is based upon an X.509 certificate.
trans-unit.target: Representa um token de segurança baseia-se após um certificado x.&509;.

trans-unit.source: To get the details of the X.509 certificate, access the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Para obter os detalhes do certificado x.&509;, aceda a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>

trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken"> </xref> classe utilizando o certificado x.&509; especificado.

trans-unit.source: Use the Certificate property to get the details about the X.509 certificate associated with the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> security token.
trans-unit.target: Utilize a propriedade de certificado para obter detalhes sobre o certificado x.&509; associada a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>token de segurança.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.target: Por exemplo, o thumbprint do certificado x.&509; pode ser acedido utilizando o <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Thumbprint%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Thumbprint%2A>

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Versões de todos os recursos utilizados pelo <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call the Dispose method when you are finished using the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar o método de Dispose quando tiver terminado de utilizando <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: The Dispose method leaves the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O método de Dispose deixa o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>num Estado não utilizável.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: After calling the Dispose method, you must release all references to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar o método de Dispose, tem de libertar todas as referências para o <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>para que o recoletor de lixo pode reclame a memória que a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>foi occupying.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call Dispose before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada eliminar antes de libertar a última referência <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está a utilizar não irão ser libertados até que as chamadas de recoletor de lixo a <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether the key identifier for this instance is equal to the specified key identifier.
trans-unit.target: Devolve um valor que indica se o identificador da chave para esta instância é igual ao identificador de chave especificado.

trans-unit.source: The MatchesKeyIdentifierClause method matches criteria in the X.509 certificate in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> property based on the type of the `keyIdentifierClause` parameter.
trans-unit.target: O método MatchesKeyIdentifierClause corresponde aos critérios do certificado x.&509; no <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>propriedade com base no tipo do `keyIdentifierClause` parâmetro.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>

trans-unit.source: The following table details what is matched.
trans-unit.target: A tabela seguinte fornece detalhes sobre o que é correspondido.

trans-unit.source: |Key identifier clause type|What is matched| |--------------------------------|---------------------| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>|The value of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A> property and the issuer serial number returned from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A> method.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause>|The data returned from the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A> method.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause>|The subject key identifier extension in the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A> property is matched.| |<xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause>|The thumbprint that is returned by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A> method.|
trans-unit.target: | Tipo de cláusula do identificador de chave | O que é correspondido | |--------------------------------|---------------------| | <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>| A propriedade <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A>e o número de série do emissor, o valor devolvido do método <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A>. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause>| Os dados devolvida do método <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A>. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause>| A extensão do identificador da chave do requerente na propriedade <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A>é correspondida. | | <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause>| O thumbprint que é devolvido pelo <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A>método. |</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetCertHash%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509ThumbprintKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.Extensions%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SubjectKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetRawCertData%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509RawDataKeyIdentifierClause> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate.GetSerialNumber%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.IssuerName%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509IssuerSerialKeyIdentifierClause>

trans-unit.source: Gets the cryptographic keys associated with the security token.
trans-unit.target: Obtém as chaves criptográficas associadas ao token de segurança.

trans-unit.source: Use the SecurityKeys property to set the cryptographic keys for this security token to protect a SOAP message.
trans-unit.target: Utilize a propriedade SecurityKeys para definir as chaves criptográficas este token de segurança proteger uma mensagem SOAP.

trans-unit.source: The keys can be used, among other things, to digitally sign or encrypt SOAP messages.
trans-unit.target: As chaves podem ser utilizadas, entre outras coisas, digitalmente iniciar sessão ou encriptar mensagens SOAP.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> of type <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityKey"></xref> that contains the set of keys associated with the security token.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> do tipo <xref href="System.IdentityModel.Tokens.SecurityKey"> </xref> que contém o conjunto de chaves associadas com o token de segurança.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first instant in time at which this security token is valid.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a primeira instantâneas no tempo no qual este token de segurança é válido.

trans-unit.source: The ValidFrom property is specified in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) and is the value of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotBefore%2A> property of the X.509 certificate specified in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade ValidFrom é especificada na hora Universal Coordenada (UTC) e é o valor da <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotBefore%2A>propriedade do certificado x.&509; especificado no <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotBefore%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.DateTime> that represents the instant in time at which this security token is first valid.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.DateTime>que representa a instantâneas no tempo no qual este token de segurança pela primeira vez é válido.</xref:System.DateTime>

trans-unit.source: Gets the last instant in time at which this security token is valid.
trans-unit.target: Obtém a última instantânea no tempo no qual este token de segurança é válido.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.ValidFrom%2A> property is specified in Coordinated Universal Time (UTC) and is the value of the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotAfter%2A> property of the X.509 certificate specified in the <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.ValidFrom%2A>propriedade é especificada na hora Universal Coordenada (UTC) e o valor a <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotAfter%2A>propriedade do certificado x.&509; especificado no <xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.Certificate%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.X509Certificates.X509Certificate2.NotAfter%2A> </xref:System.IdentityModel.Tokens.X509SecurityToken.ValidFrom%2A>
